        {
            "title": "星島獨家｜政府針對美國關稅 召開人大及政協專題座談會 由李家超主持",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"政府今午（17日）召開港區全國人大代表及全國政協委員專題座談會\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e32b84dc17be49a28ba0e0a8332325e9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250417/_2025041715255086972.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">政府今午（17日）召開港區全國人大代表及全國政協委員專題座談會</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>《星島頭條》記者獨家接獲消息，政府今午（17日）召開港區全國人大代表及全國政協委員專題座談會。據了解，今次座談會約1個半小時，主題針對如何應對美國關稅戰，由行政長官李家超主持。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200502/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"蔡冠深。郭詠欣攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/86135c662f585e194ffee7233c29766a/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250417_151424300_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蔡冠深。郭詠欣攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200503/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"邱達昌。郭詠欣攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d8dfe76da8f1b5844c6bfca37d63044f/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250417_151513565_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        邱達昌。郭詠欣攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200504/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鄺美雲。郭詠欣攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/76efa77e37cb05475b21cb09608842e7/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250417_151620315_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄺美雲。郭詠欣攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200505/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"郭詠欣攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/562ebf0cacc05c3d942658bee81387d7/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250417_151620315_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        郭詠欣攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200506/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"盧金榮。郭詠欣攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b17e4c1fcdd56d3ddfd7dacd6a0522b3/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250417_151620315_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        盧金榮。郭詠欣攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>今午2時許，多名港區人大政協陸續現身政府總部，包括港區人大代表陳帆、徐莉、文穎怡、鄺美雲，政協常委邱達昌、身兼中華總商會會長蔡冠深、身兼廠商會會長及政協委員會盧金榮等，座談會於政總地下演講廳舉行。\n\n</p>\n<p>據了解，今次除了政府與人大政協商討目前本港最新形勢外，亦會聆聽各人大政協有何意見，以讓香港更好應對美國關稅戰帶來的局勢，預料部分人可獲發言機會。\n\n</p>\n<p>記者：郭詠欣\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
