        {
            "title": "珍惜生命｜藍田康田苑男子墮樓 當場不治",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警員調查死者墮樓位置。劉漢權攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a46d3dafe595b51ec7de8eb7b861c503/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250417/_2025041714351960697.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警員調查死者墮樓位置。劉漢權攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（17日）下午1時34分，警方接報指藍田康田苑有人墮樓。救援人員趕到，發現男事主已當場不治，其身份及事故原因有待調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200318/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員調查死者墮樓位置。劉漢權攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5a41ec88d9fc137087a3dd34fb9df449/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250417_140714475_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員調查死者墮樓位置。劉漢權攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200319/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"人員在場調查。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/46b4d7388fbae4f89f34357e722d4348/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250417_140714475_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"medi