        {
            "title": "NBA附加賽｜獨行俠120:106勝帝王 將與灰熊爭西岸第8種子席位",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"獨行俠120:106勝帝王，將與灰熊爭西岸第8種子席位。AP\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a4c2f6a349daa13f3b63071bdec9beb9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250417/_2025041714173318362.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">獨行俠120:106勝帝王，將與灰熊爭西岸第8種子席位。AP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>奇利湯遜(Klay Thompson)去年常規賽附加賽代表勇士對帝王，成為勇士出局罪人，今次他轉披獨行俠戰衣於附加賽再戰帝王上演復仇戰，在關鍵的第2次攻入16分，助獨行俠單節贏25分奠下勝基。獨行俠最終作客120:106擊敗帝王晉級，將於周五與灰熊爭奪西岸第8種子的最後一個季後賽席位。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"獨行俠(左)淘汰帝王(右)晉級附加賽次圈。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e145e7ed632646d314bddb1a893c509a/2025-04/Mavericks_Kings_Basketball_02337--e7b70.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        獨行俠(左)淘汰帝王(右)晉級附加賽次圈。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安東尼戴維斯(右)首次代表獨行俠出戰附加賽。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2ec29e83f6ddf7c4366000d82f90b273/2025-04/Mavericks_Kings_Basketball_88517--b0d99.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安東尼戴維斯(右)首次代表獨行俠出戰附加賽。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"獨行俠(上)淘汰帝王晉級附加賽次圈。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ebfa0e346908a187d25df2849f3a8478/2025-04/Mavericks_Kings_Basketball_02020--eee60.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        獨行俠(上)淘汰帝王晉級附加賽次圈。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"獨行俠(上)淘汰帝王晉級附加賽次圈。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/02ddd9c77d9a974a89ea6c049ef97d79/2025-04/APTOPIX_Mavericks_Kings_Basketball_29560--13aa1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        獨行俠(上)淘汰帝王晉級附加賽次圈。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"奇利湯遜(右)3分起手。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f2c4f57c857d21f22257f245021c09f0/2025-04/Mavericks_Kings_Basketball_65007--fb040.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奇利湯遜(右)3分起手。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"帝王球員在對手包圍下強行上籃。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c6138dea79cfaf1281b2633e077c32fc/2025-04/Mavericks_Kings_Basketball_82419--520d3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        帝王球員在對手包圍下強行上籃。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"奇利湯遜擊敗帝王成功復仇。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/189621378ae54836f23ffe9b932be758/2025-04/Mavericks_Kings_Basketball_23588--1f5b8.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奇利湯遜擊敗帝王成功復仇。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"奇利湯遜擊敗帝王成功復仇。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/82405c95bbb877d9ea72d3bb514bba91/2025-04/Mavericks_Kings_Basketball_48740--e1a1d.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奇利湯遜擊敗帝王成功復仇。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>獨行俠晉級與灰熊爭西岸第8種子</h2>\n<p>上季西岸附加賽首圈第9名帝王主場對第10名的勇士，奇利湯遜10投全炒連累勇士以94:118落敗被帝王淘汰出局。冤家路窄，奇利湯遜在今季西岸附加賽首圈再次遇上帝王，改披獨行俠戰衣的奇利湯遜今仗大打爭氣波，於第2節投進4個3分球，攻入個入23分中的16分，助獨行俠於第2次打出44:19，單節赢25分，帶著23分的領先優勢進入下半場，早早奠定勝局。\n\n</p><h2>帝王近19季僅1次入季後賽</h2>\n<p>獨行俠下半場談笑用兵下，仍以14分擊敗帝王順利晉級，奇利湯遜總算成功復仇。而獨行俠淘汰帝王後將與附加賽首圈敗給勇士的常規賽西岸第8位灰熊，爭奪西岸第8種子席位。至於帝王今仗雖然有迪羅辛攻入全場最高的33分，小沙邦尼斯亦有11分和13個籃板的雙雙成績亦難逃輸波出局。帝王經歷12月炒教練米克布朗，以及2月換走明星後衛迪艾朗霍斯後實力大減，遭逢過去19季第18次無緣季後賽。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064435/即時-體育-NBA附加賽-獨行俠120-106勝帝王-將與灰熊爭西岸第8種子席位",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 14:36:17",
