        {
            "title": "深水埗單車賊偷配件斷正發難 物主被追打匿巴士車底受傷",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"單車物主一度匿入巴士車底。劉漢權攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/24d7ce7b3fdb8f7f721b7125c4818ac5/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250417/_2025041714080883079.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">單車物主一度匿入巴士車底。劉漢權攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（17日）早上11時許，一名疑似癮君子的男子在深水埗南昌街近荔枝角道交界，懷疑拆去綁在鐵欄邊一輛單車的座椅，企圖偷走。其間單車的物主發現，連忙上前喝止，並與對方發生爭執。未料賊人突然發難追打物主，物主連忙逃走，一直走到荔枝角道265號對開，慌亂中更匿入路邊一輛九巴的車底。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方最初接報指有巴士撞倒途人，到場後始發現事件不涉交通意外，事主已由巴士車底自行爬出。人員經調查後，以涉嫌襲擊拘捕涉案賊人。單車物主手腳擦傷，事後由救護車送往明愛醫院治理。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200274/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"男子涉嫌襲擊被捕。劉漢權攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dd7b9155200ba27d4e18fc2606b6a77e/2025-04/1_37.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男子涉嫌襲擊被捕。劉漢權攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200275/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"單車物主擦傷手腳，由救護車送院。劉漢權攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9c071beaa1bde0dcf7416631a29fe14f/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250417_125311008.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單車物主擦傷手腳，由救護車送院。劉漢權攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200264/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"單車被賊人拆去座椅。劉漢權攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bba1a96d1f7958b5bcfa61de3332a6aa/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250417_123148463.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單車被賊人拆去座椅。劉漢權攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200265/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員在場調查。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/da5ff5c7a5a243535f756343e3dda6e6/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250417_123148463_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員在場調查。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200266/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/61b473865eb71bcf4b62fa4525cc2021/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250417_123148463_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200267/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f283db7fad01105cea2b2ebdab8653dc/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250417_123148463_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200268/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"單車物主一度匿入巴士車底。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3cd4b4a6ae016b513953edcbf6e1e142/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250417_123148463_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單車物主一度匿入巴士車底。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4200269/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"單車物主一度匿入巴士車底。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f2183850737a97998aca5fd492462199/2025-04/Ka